{"tid":2043023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一個朝早兩單新聞證實：香港有國安+司法黑暗時代","createTime":"2020-05-30T06:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T13:08:07.000Z","uid":7542,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e1676dbcbc29557c2f3b84d384fa23e84fc382a0","tid":2043023,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:49:53.000Z","msg":"啲人成日都話唔好講嘢冇證冇據<br />\n今日一個朝頭早兩單新聞證實晒所有嘢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>新聞1: </strong></span><strong>李家超：中央有向警隊提供情報協助制定戰術</strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>中央在很多層面上都掌握香港情況，有向特區提供情報...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://share.881903.com/?news_id=1294211&amp;category_id=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshare.881903.com%2F%3Fnews_id%3D1294211%26category_id%3D0&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=e507a5e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://share.881903.com/?news_id=1294211&amp;category_id=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>新聞2: </strong></span><strong>中國所做的一切，律政司既不知亦看不見 </strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>BBC：銅鑼灣書店員工失蹤之後現身大陸的事件，令全社會擔心《國安法》被強行推出後，如果再有人賣禁書得罪北京當局，他們的結局會是什麼？<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊：我想重申，有關你提及的案件，那一起事件，我們不知道發生什麼事。<br />\n<br />\nBBC：過往有大陸案例、喊「結束一黨專政」、官員下台、要求黨負責，在大陸可能面臨刑事處罰，那法例通過之後，香港市民以後還可以再喊這些口號嗎？<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊：我唔清楚<br />\n<br />\nBBC：「港獨」口號會否被抓？示威權利會否被減少？<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊：不能保證</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-52852257\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-52852257&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=afa9c3ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-52852257&h=c859d4e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-52852257</a><br />\n<br />\n再比對吓過往極權國家嘅手段 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F-SKS89xxRg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF-SKS89xxRg&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=2b5aa05c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F-SKS89xxRg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BufF8VPWDZg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBufF8VPWDZg&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=c037d494\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BufF8VPWDZg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n^希望大家可以睇一睇，我已經盡量將歷史資料壓縮同埋簡化，希望大家可以容易消化！連登係好多人都有差唔多嘅睇法，但係外面嘅人未必係。希望巴絲打鍾意條片嘅請 CLSS，最重要係廣傳！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>We shall outmaneuver them.</em></strong><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 睇完片之後有咩問題想問，歡迎喺呢度或者係片下面留言，我會逐一回覆！"},{"pid":"e135ff817fcd4b6316d91753ffdd26240038cb49","tid":2043023,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:51:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4f8f0678ac785d8b685d9444314a685e926db3e4","tid":2043023,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:54:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c1221723eab8e6bda8138682648a277bbca5164a","tid":2043023,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40ba85016746f92a210f7912d71a084836acb94","tid":2043023,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d0feb71b2008d3009312b7712ce88c15840e64","tid":2043023,"uid":111322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:57:13.000Z","msg":"唔做戲了"},{"pid":"ef2e66913fc75ca202f9eb06200b3a4b1918a9b9","tid":2043023,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},